title: The Black Dots of Death - Ever Since We Were Children (Album) +
description:
Wassup

I was looking all over the internet for this album, but I found out all the torrents are dead and all links broken. So I downloaded each music separately from YouTube (which can be a pain in the ass compared to simply downloading a torrent) and put it all together.

This is not exactly as the album, as originally there are only 9 tracks plus the 3 bonus ones (which are not included here), but I took the oportunity to add 'Let's get fucked up', which is a great song btw, and tagged it as track 10.

Well, enjoy. That's some great shit.




Music by The Black Dots of Death, 2011.
